examples.en: His gestures provided eloquent reinforcement for his complaints.
He has a gallery of flamboyant gestures that makes him easy to imitate.
The rebels' pacific gestures have met with little response from the army.
Specific gestures can indicate particular moods.
The government thinks it can get away with token gestures on environmental issues.
